    "body": "This issue requires the addition of middleware on metamask-mobile to ensure that there is no impact to the dapp API, because the nonce tracker middleware in `web3-provider-engine` being replaced also has a dapp-facing impact. The impact is that the `eth_getTransactionCount` will include pending transactions in the count returned if you ask for the `pending` block.\r\n\r\nThis feature has been implemented on mobile in this branch: https://github.com/MetaMask/metamask-mobile/tree/refactor-get-transaction-count\r\n\r\nIt needs to be rebased and it needs to be tested, but otherwise it's just blocked by this transaction controller work.",
